## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="f570a-306">에 대 한 정보를 기록 하는 다음 예제는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> 개체는 [콘솔](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=159613)합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f570a-306">The following example writes information about a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object to the [console](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=159613).</span></span>  

```csharp  

private static void DumpGrammarStatus(Grammar item)  
{  
  Console.WriteLine("Grammar name is {0}:", item.Name);  
  Console.WriteLine("  The Grammar {0} loaded.",  
    item.Loaded ? "is" : "is not");  
  Console.WriteLine("  The Grammar {0} enabled.",  
    item.Enabled ? "is" : "is not");  
  if (item.RuleName != null)  
  {  
    Console.WriteLine("  The root rule is {0}.", item.RuleName);  
  }  
  else  
  {  
    Console.WriteLine("  The Grammar does not specify a root rule.");  
  }  
}  
```



